            Discover a winning lineup of fashion-forward gear that allows you to express your love for the game in every aspect of your life. From iconic jerseys to street-style essentials, we've got your wardrobe covered, ensuring you're always on top of your style game.
        </h5>
    </div>
    <br>

    <div class="row">
        <h4>Quality Meets Fandom: </h4>
        <h5>
            We understand that being a fan is not just about the game; it's a lifestyle. That's why we source premium materials and collaborate with top designers to bring you products that seamlessly blend quality, comfort, and team pride. Each piece is a celebration of your favorite teams and players.
        </h5>
    </div>
    <br>

    <h4>Explore Our Exclusive Collection:</h4> <br> <br>

    <div class="row pb-3">
        @foreach (var product in Model)
        {
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 mb-3">
                <div class="card border-0 p-3 shadow rounded">
                    <img src="@product.ImageUrl" class="card-img-top rounded" />
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-title text-opacity-75 text-center overflow-hidden" style="white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;">
                            @product.Name
                        </p><br>
                        <p class="text-opacity-75 text-center">
                            Price: <span>@product.Price.ToString("c")</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <a asp-action="ProductDetails" asp-route-productId="@product.ProductId" class="btn btn-primary bg-gradient border-0 form-control">
                            Details
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        }
    </div>
</div>
